{"title":"孔繁森同志诗歌选抄","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":4,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔繁森同志诗歌选抄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编者按"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔繁森同志两次赴西藏工作共有近十年时间，写了许多抒发人生志向和对藏族同胞一片真情的诗篇。翻阅这些诗词，一个人民公仆忠于党、忠于祖国、忠于人民的情怀跃然纸上。我们从他的遗作中摘选刊登，以飨读者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峥嵘岁月三十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二次出征到边关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏遍荒山犹未老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历尽千辛更知甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰山愈冷情愈热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿耿忠心照雪山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拭泪辞亲赴西界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银装蜡象夫莫开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依别情谁为寄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拳拳赤子何由来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除夕猝增思亲意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却非素日铁石心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺氧带来体失重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盈雪净化凌魄魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今逢佳节在异乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉藏新友聚一堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党业民托牢牢记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除夕之夜话沧桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满城酥油散幽香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风袅袅拂面凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈步大街闲消遣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"异族风光趣味长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写给武警退伍老战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生道路多坎坷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下众生苦求索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世代沧桑万变化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风浪之中看万波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千河万川争奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志士杰人踏险峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风求索，雨求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦求索，乐求索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几多烦恼，几多欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹉跎岁月，岁月蹉跎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝君前进路上奋进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激流之中看豪杰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜静四无邻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犬声扰我心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思乡思亲友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更思老母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜风雨寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情怀自觉暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思乡随月走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众托记心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不负党教诲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我志献高原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新诗如有翼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞至东昌边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞上曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远征西涯整十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦乐桑梓在高原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为万家能团圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九天云外有青山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿里情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四五高原雪满山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹乱石击蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛夏难寻芳草绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中常品红枣甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咏红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无垠戈壁绿一层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历尽沧桑骨殷红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因根生大漠下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢笑翠柏与青松。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}